_header: If thou wilt go in to the parts of the east
_description: Prognostics by the moon for a journey — four couplets

BodAsh210.First Lines:
[ ]to the partes of the este[ ]s in a signe ventose that is
                    weste…
BodAsh210.Last Lines:
…[ ]f þou wylt goo into the sowthe go[ ]yng in a signe
                    waterly & northe
BodAsh210.Note: The folio is damaged and the beginnings of lines are lost.
